dc_description_s: Alternate title: Stadtplan von Nottingham mit militaergeographischen Eintragungen. Grossblatt 6, Blattbereich 17. Relief shown by 25 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Gauss-Krueger grid. Legend is in English and German. With a list of abbreviations. Source: Ordnance Survey 1:10,560. Accompanied by 66p. booklet: "Militaergeographische Einzelangaben ueber England; Objektbilder zu den militaergeographischen Objektkarten 1:250 000 und 1:10 000 der Mappe 6 Nord-Midlands"; of photographs and drawings of important military objectives, bridges, factories, etc. (sites are located on map). This sheet is from the series Zusamendruck (compress) edition. This sheet is from the series Zusamendruck (compress) edition.
dc_publisher_s: Berlin : Generalstab des Heeres, Abt. für Kriegskarten und Vermessungswesen, IV. Mil. Geo., 1942.
